	*</PropValue>
	
	PROCEDURE anychange		&& Called from both InteractiveChange and ProgrammaticChange to consolidate handling any changes
		* Abstract method
		
	ENDPROC

	PROCEDURE Init
		With This
			.FontName = ccFontSizeName
